Package view

Interface ISimulaattorinUI

All Known Implementing Classes:
SimulaattorinGUI
public interface ISimulaattorinUI
Interface for the graphical user interface of the simulator. The controller gets input from the user interface, which it forwards to the OmaMoottori class.
